	   <tr><td colspan=2>Another reason many of the Velious weapons are no drop, is because Verant intended Velious to be a 30+ expansion.  Now of course there are players like yourself and others who are surviving and holding your own in Velious, but most everyone else still in their teens is over on Antonica or Kunark.  Verant probably made most of the weapons no drop in order to reduce the number of lower level players coming to Velious, the good nodrop weapons are too hard to get and the bad nodrop weapons are worthless.  Really if you think about it, with 4 continents you can use, a lack of a few new no drop weapons really isn't a problem.<br><br>Note: Just for clerification, No drop weapons doesn't help on PvP, no one can loot primary, secondary, or any ranged slot off of your corpse.<br><br>Gedran<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
